---
title: Thai Style Pork Meatballs on Flatbreads with Sesame Sweet Potato Wedges and Peanut Butter Drizzle
description: These Thai Style Pork Meatballs on Flatbreads are a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-style-pork-meatballs-on-flatbreads-2b144b24-6ad6b132.jpg
